font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-187" data-semantic-type="fence" data-semantic-role="close" data-semantic-id="67" data-semantic-parent="68" data-semantic-operator="fenced" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-188" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="88" data-semantic-parent="89" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="msub" id="MathJax-Span-189" data-semantic-type="subscript" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-id="71" data-semantic-children="69,70" data-semantic-parent="89" data-semantic-complexity="6.6" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-197" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="74" data-semantic-parent="76" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-198" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="75" data-semantic-parent="76" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-199" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="77" data-semantic-parent="93" data-semantic-operator="multirel" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-200" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="78" data-semantic-parent="93" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.264em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.748em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.103em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">
y=\left(\cos^{-1}{x}\right)^2\Rightarrow y_1=2\cos^{-1}{x}.  \frac{-1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}\\
\Rightarrow\left(1-x^2\right)y_1^2=4y\Rightarrow\left(1-x^2\right)y_2-xy_1=2 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-838" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="74" data-semantic-children="73,69" data-semantic-content="68" data-semantic-parent="75" data-semantic-complexity="15"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-839" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="73" data-semantic-children="65,66,67" data-semantic-content="71,72" data-semantic-parent="74" data-semantic-complexity="10"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-840" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="65" data-semantic-parent="73" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-843" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="72" data-semantic-parent="73" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-844" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="67" data-semantic-parent="73" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-845" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="68" data-semantic-parent="74" data-semantic-operator="infixop,−" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-846" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="69" data-semantic-parent="74" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-847" data-semantic-type="fence" data-semantic-role="close" data-semantic-id="70" data-semantic-parent="75" data-semantic-operator="fenced" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.03em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.035em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.297em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.052em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-28">x^y=e^{x+y}\Rightarrow ylnx=x+y 
\Rightarrow\frac{y}{x}+lnx\frac{dy}{dx}=1+\frac{dy}{dx}\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{x-y}{x(lnx-1)} 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="therefore t equals 2 s" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-958" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="8" data-semantic-children="5,7" data-semantic-content="2" data-semantic-complexity="14" style="width: 3.65em; padding-left: 0.289em;">t</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-963" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="2" data-semantic-parent="8" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-964" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="7" data-semantic-children="3,4" data-semantic-content="6" data-semantic-parent="8" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-965" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-parent="7" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-966" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="6" data-semantic-parent="7" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-967" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="4" data-semantic-parent="7" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-42">
y=\ln(secx+tanx) 
\therefore\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{secxtanx+\sec^2{x}}{secx+tanx}=secx

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="f left-parenthesis x right-parenthesis" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1177" data-semantic-type="appl" data-semantic-role="simple function" data-semantic-id="6" data-semantic-children="0,4" data-semantic-content="5,0" data-semantic-complexity="11" style="width: 2.573em; \left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{-\frac{1}{x}}\Rightarrow lny=\ -   \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}  \frac{\ln{\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)}}{x}\\

\Rightarrow lny=\ - \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}  x\left(-\frac{1}{x^2}\right)= \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim} \frac{1}{x}</script></span></p>

border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.402em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-59">\therefore y= \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{-\ 1/x}=1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-72">\underset{x\rightarrow\infty}{\lim} \left(\frac{x}{x+1}\right)^{-3x}= \underset{x\rightarrow\infty}{\lim}  \left(1+\frac{1}{x}\right)^{3x}=e^3</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 13 </span>

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-89-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="x equals 1" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2137" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-children="0,2" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="width: 2.908em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: "></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>x&nbsp;এর কোন মানের জন্য&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-99-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="y equals collapsed product with 2 factors" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2394" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="14" data-semantic-children="0,13" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="width: 7.975em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.522em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1006.41em, 2.61em, -999.998em); \frac{dy}{dx}=3x^2-12=0\Rightarrow x=\pm2 
</script></span></p>

data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="143" data-semantic-parent="146" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">b</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3163" data-semantic-type="fence" data-semantic-role="close" data-semantic-id="147" data-semantic-parent="148" data-semantic-operator="fenced" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.797em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.548em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.603em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-124">f^1\left(x\right)=-a^2\sin{\left(ax+b\right)}=a^2\cos{\left(\frac{\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)} \\
f^2\left(x\right)=-a^3\sin{\left(\frac{\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)}=a^3\cos{\left(\frac{2\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)} \\
f^3\left(x\right)=-a^4\sin{\left(2.\frac{\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)}=a^4\cos{\left(\frac{3\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)}
</script></span></p>

data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="92" data-semantic-parent="94" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3309" data-semantic-complexity="1.5"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3310"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3311" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="93" data-semantic-parent="94" data-semantic-complexity="1.5" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">11</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3312" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="122" data-semantic-parent="123" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3313" data-semantic-type="appl" data-semantic-role="prefix function" data-semantic-id="99" data-semantic-children="95,97" data-semantic-content="98,95" data-semantic-parent="123" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3314" data-semantic-type="function" data-semantic-role="prefix function" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="95" data-semantic-parent="99" data-semantic-operator="appl" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">cos</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3315" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="application" data-semantic-id="98" data-semantic-parent="99" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="appl" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3316" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3317"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3318" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="97" data-semantic-parent="99" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.674em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.452em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-125">\therefore f^n\left(x\right)=a^{n+1}\cos{\left(\frac{n\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)} \\
\therefore f^{10}\left(x\right)=a^{11}\cos{\left(\frac{10\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)}=-a^{11}\cos{\left(ax+b\right)} \\
\therefore f^{10}\left(0\right)=-a^{11}\cos{b} 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                            <div class="row" style="margin-top:20px;">
                                <h2>Physics (16)</h2>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 19 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>দুটি সমান দৈর্ঘ্যের&nbsp;&nbsp;তারের ব্যাস যথাক্রমে&nbsp;2mm&nbsp;ও&nbsp;5mm.&nbsp;এদের সমান বলে টানা হলে প্রথম তারটির দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি দ্বিতীয়টির 4&nbsp;গুণ হয়। কোন তারটি অধিক স্থিতিস্থাপক?</p>

                                        </div>

font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3460" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="31" data-semantic-parent="32" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-131">
\frac{1}{k\prime}=\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{k}+\frac{1}{k}  \therefore k^\prime=\frac{k}{5} 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 22 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>স্থির লিফটে কোনো সরল দোলকের দোলনকাল T ।&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-140-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="StartFraction g Over 4 EndFraction" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3589" data-semantic-complexity="5.2" style="width: 0.859em; data-semantic-id="64" data-semantic-parent="65" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3779" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="66" data-semantic-parent="82" data-semantic-operator="infixop,×" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3780" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="67" data-semantic-parent="82" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1.2</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3781" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="68" data-semantic-parent="85" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3782" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="84" data-semantic-children="69,70" data-semantic-content="83" data-semantic-parent="85" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3783" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="69" data-semantic-parent="84" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1.7</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3784" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="83" data-semantic-parent="84" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3785" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="70" data-semantic-parent="84" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.65em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.548em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.053em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-146">T_1=\frac{60}{50}=1.2s\ ;\ \ T\propto\sqrt L\Rightarrow\ \frac{T_2}{T_1}=\sqrt{\frac{L_2}{L_1}}=\sqrt{\frac{2L_1}{L_1}}=\sqrt2\\ 

\Rightarrow\ T_2=\sqrt2\times T_1=\sqrt2 \times 1.2=1.7s </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 25 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি ফাঁপা গোলককে পানি দিয়ে পূর্ণ করে একটি সুতার সাহায্যে ঝুলিয়ে সরল দোলক তৈরি করা হল। এখন, গোলকের তলায় ছিদ্র করে দিলে যদি পানি পড়তে থাকে তাহলে প্রাথমিকভাবে দোলনকালের কী পরিবর্তন হবে?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>একই থাকবে</p>
</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group AnsTrue" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">B</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>বাড়বে</p>
</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">C</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>কমবে</p>
</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>None</p>
</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বাড়বে; কারণ, পানি পড়তে থাকলে গোলকের ভরকেন্দ্র নিচে নামতে থাকবে, ফলে কার্যকরী দৈর্ঘ্য বৃদ্ধি পাবে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>কোনটিই নয়</p>
</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 28 </span>
                                            <span style="float: right !important; border-bottom:0px; color: "></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 180px; height: 86px;"></p>

<p>চিত্রের মতো করে 2m দীর্ঘ AB তারের মধ্যবিন্দুতে 5 kg ভরের বস্তু ঝুলালে তারটি আনুভূমিকের সাথে 10° করে নিচে নেমে যায়। এক্ষেত্রে তারের ইয়ং এর গুণাঙ্ক&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-156-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="2 times collapsed product with 3 factors" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4032" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="14" data-semantic-children="0,13" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="width: 7.64em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.261em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1006.26em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4033"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4034" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="14" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4035" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="14" data-semantic-operator="infixop,×" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 180px; height: 90px;"></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-161-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed semicolon separated list of length 3" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4102" style="width: 20.166em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: 0em;"><span class="maction" id="MJX-Collapse-309" data-semantic-complexity="2"><span class="MathJax_HitBox" id="MathJax-HitBox-4103" style="border: 0px none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; \ \therefore l^\prime=\frac{1}{cos⁡(10°)}=1.015m \\ \therefore L^\prime=2l^\prime=2\times1.015=2.031\ m \\ \therefore ∆l=L'-L=0.031 m ; Y=2×10^{11}Nm^{-2} \\ \therefore Y=\frac{FL}{A\Delta l}\Rightarrow A=\frac{FL}{Y\Delta l}=1.58\times{10}^{-8}\\ \Rightarrow r=\sqrt{\frac{A}{\pi}} \therefore r=7.09\times{10}^{-5}m=0.07\ mm \rm </script></span></p>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 29 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>Y&nbsp;স্থিতিস্থাপক গুণাঙ্কের কোনো তারে P&nbsp;পীড়ন প্রয়োগে একক আয়তনে সঞ্চিত স্থিতিশক্তি কত হবে?</p>

                                            <span>Question 31 </span>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4927" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="24" data-semantic-parent="30" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4928" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="25" data-semantic-parent="30" data-semantic-operator="multirel" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="maction" id="MJX-Collapse-357" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="MathJax_HitBox" id="MathJax-HitBox-4929" style="border: 0px none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 3.281em; height: 0.699em; vertical-align: -0.039em; margin-right: -3.277em; cursor: pointer;"></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4930" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="26" data-semantic-parent="30" data-semantic-complexity="4" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; cursor: pointer;">235.514</span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4931" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="31" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4932" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="27" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4933" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="32" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4934" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="28" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.092em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-181">\frac{2}{2.14}=\frac{3600-n}{3600}\Rightarrow3600-n=\frac{2\times3600}{2.14}=3364.486 
\Rightarrow n=235.514\ s 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <span>Question 34 </span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

M=44.01\approx44\ g\ mole^{-1} </script></span></p>

<p>সুতরাং, গ্যাসটির আণবিক ভর&nbsp;&nbsp;44&nbsp;g&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-213-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="therefore" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5417" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1000.49em, 2.42em, -999.998em); display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-214-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="upper C upper O 2" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5420" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="0,3" data-semantic-content="4" data-semantic-complexity="11.6" style="width: 1.969em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1001.6em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5421"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5422" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block;                                 </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 41 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>1L,&nbsp;3L,&nbsp;4L&nbsp;আয়তনের তিনটি পাত্র একটি নির্দিষ্ট তাপমাত্রায় যথাক্রমে&nbsp;4,&nbsp;4&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;6atm&nbsp;চাপে গ্যাস দ্বারা পূর্ণ। পাত্র 3&nbsp;টি পরস্পর সংযুক্ত করলে গ্যাসের মোট চাপ কত &nbsp;হবে?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 42 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 137px;"></p>

<p>&nbsp;লেখচিত্রটি কোন সূত্রকে সমর্থন করে?&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-228-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="left-bracket collapsed inequality sequence with 3 elements right-bracket" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5875" data-semantic-type="fenced" data-semantic-role="leftright" data-semantic-id="14" data-semantic-children="13" data-semantic-content="0,12" data-semantic-complexity="7.5" style="width: 7.826em;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 44 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নির্দিষ্ট তাপমাত্রা ও চাপে একটি সরু ছিদ্র দিয়ে একটি অজ্ঞাত গ্যাসের নিঃসরণ হার ঐ একই ছিদ্র দিয়ে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-230-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="upper C upper O 2" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5987" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="0,3" data-semantic-content="4" data-semantic-complexity="11.6" style="width: 2.386em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.939em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1001.94em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5988"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5989" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-6040" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="34" data-semantic-parent="38" data-semantic-complexity="1.5" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">44</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.95em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.49em;"><span class="msub" id="MathJax-Span-6041" data-semantic-type="subscript" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-id="37" data-semantic-children="35,36" data-semantic-parent="38" data-semantic-complexity="6.6"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-6042" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="35" data-semantic-parent="37" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.07em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-6044" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="arrow" data-semantic-id="39" data-semantic-parent="45" data-semantic-operator="multirel" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="msub" id="MathJax-Span-6045" data-semantic-type="subscript" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-id="42" data-semantic-children="40,41" data-semantic-parent="45" data-semantic-complexity="6.6" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-6046" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="40" data-semantic-parent="42" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-6047" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="41" data-semantic-parent="42" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-6048" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="43" data-semantic-parent="45" data-semantic-operator="multirel" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-6049" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="44" data-semantic-parent="45" data-semantic-complexity="2.5" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2.08</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.461em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-231">\frac{r_x}{r_{CO_2}}=\sqrt{\frac{m_{CO_2}}{m_x}}\Rightarrow\left(4.6\right)^2=\frac{44}{m_x}\Rightarrow m_x=2.08 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-238-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed equality sequence with 4 elements" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-6086" style="width: 12.748em; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.863em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -6.147em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 7.053em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-244">P_1=P_2,\ V_1=V_2 \\ \therefore n_1R T_1=n_2RT_2\Rightarrow \frac{w_1}{m}\times R\times T_1=\frac{w_2}{m}\times R\times T_2 \\ \Rightarrow w_1T_1=w_2T_2\Rightarrow w_2=\frac{w_1T_1}{T_2}=\frac{15\times 298}{303}=14.75g \\ \therefore ∆w=w_1-w_2=0.25g </script></span></p>

</span>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-261-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed separator separated list of length 1" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-6652" style="width: 3.773em; id="MathJax-Element-265">\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{12}\left(4x^3-14\times3x^2+72\times2x-162\right)=0 \\
\Rightarrow4x^3-42x^2+144x-162=0\Rightarrow\left(x-3\right)^2\ (2x-9)=0 \\
\therefore x=3\ ;\ x=\frac{9}{2} 
\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}=\frac{1}{12}({12x}^2-84x+144) \\
f^{\prime\prime}\left(3\right)=0; \\ \ f^{\prime\prime}\left(\frac{9}{2}\right)=\frac{3}{4} \\
\therefore\frac{d^3y}{dx^3}=\frac{1}{12}(24x-84) \\
f^{\prime\prime\prime}\left(3\right)=-1\neq0 
</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-266-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="therefore x equals 3" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-7011" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="4,3" data-semantic-content="2" data-semantic-complexity="9" style="width: 3.404em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.789em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.436em, 1002.75em, 2.42em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7012"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7013" data-semantic-type="prefixop" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="4" data-semantic-children="1" data-semantic-content="0" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="4"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7014" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="4" data-semantic-operator="prefixop,∴" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7015" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="4" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-266">\therefore x=3 </script></span>&nbsp;বিন্দুটি Point of inflection.</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-267-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="x equals nine-halves" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-7018" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="0,4" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="10.2" style="width: 2.666em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7019"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7020" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7021" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><b>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</b></p>

<p>সর্বোচ্চ এবং সর্বনিম্ন মান নির্ণয়ের জন্য ০২ নম্বর।</p>

<p><strong>বি:দ্রঃ&nbsp;</strong>যুক্তিসংগত যে কোনো নিয়ম গ্রহনযোগ্য।</p>

                                            </div>
                                            


                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                                        <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 2</span>
                                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>10 মিটারের একটি লম্বা সুতাকে কেটে দুইভাগ করা হল। একটি অংশ দিয়ে একটি বর্গ তৈরি করা হল এবং অপর অংশ দিয়ে একটি বৃত্ত তৈরি করা হল। কর্তিত সুতার অংশদ্বয়ের প্রত্যেকের দৈর্ঘ্য কত হলে এদের দ্বারা সৃষ্ট ক্ষেত্রের যোগফল সর্বনিম্ন বা সর্বোচ্চ হয়?</p>

                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block; border:1px solid solid; padding:0px;">
                                                            <div style="border: 1px solid solid; padding: 0px;">
                                                                
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                            <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                                <p>ধরি, 1: k অনুপাত সুতাটিকে কাটা হয়।</p>

top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7616"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7617" data-semantic-type="empty" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-complexity="0"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7618" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7619" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="1,2" data-semantic-content="4" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-7620" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7621" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="4" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7622" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="2" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-292-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="equals 4.4 m" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-7623" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="6" data-semantic-children="3,5" data-semantic-content="0" data-semantic-complexity="11" style="width: 3.199em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.625em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1002.58em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7624"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7625" data-semantic-type="empty" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-complexity="0"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7626" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7627" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="1,2" data-semantic-content="4" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-complexity="7" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-7628" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="float" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4.4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7629" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="4" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7630" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="2" data-semantic-parent="5" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-292">=4.4m </script></span>&nbsp;নির্ণয়ের জন্য ০২ নম্বর।</p>

<p><strong>বি:দ্রঃ&nbsp;</strong>যুক্তিসংগত যে কোনো নিয়ম গ্রহনযোগ্য। একক না লিখলে বা লিখে ভুল করলে ০১ নম্বর কাটা যাবে।</p>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7895" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="120" data-semantic-parent="154" data-semantic-operator="infixop,−" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-7896" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="153" data-semantic-children="121,122" data-semantic-content="152" data-semantic-parent="154" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7897" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="121" data-semantic-parent="153" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-7898" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="152" data-semantic-parent="153" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7899" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="122" data-semantic-parent="153" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.428em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.252em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-296">t=e^{m\ ln\ x}=e^{\ln{x^m}}=x^m \therefore x=e^\frac{y}{x^m}\Rightarrow\ln{x}=\frac{y}{x^m}\\ \Rightarrow y=x^m\ln{x} \therefore y_1=mx^{m-1}\ln{x}+x^{m-1}\\ \Rightarrow xy_1=mx^m\ln{x}+x^m\Rightarrow xy_1=my+x^m\Rightarrow x^m=xy_1-my </script></span></p>

<p>আবার,&nbsp;</p>

id="MathJax-Span-8375" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="321" data-semantic-children="315,320" data-semantic-content="316" data-semantic-parent="323" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="316" data-semantic-parent="321" data-semantic-operator="infixop,−" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-8378" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="implicit" data-semantic-id="320" data-semantic-children="317,318" data-semantic-content="319" data-semantic-parent="321" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-8379" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="317" data-semantic-parent="320" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-8380" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="319" data-semantic-parent="320" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-8381" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="318" data-semantic-parent="320" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-8382" data-semantic-type="fence" data-semantic-role="close" data-semantic-id="322" data-semantic-parent="323" data-semantic-operator="fenced" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-8383" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="324" data-semantic-parent="430" data-semantic-operator="multirel" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-8384" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="325" data-semantic-parent="430" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 9.428em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -11.447em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 12.553em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-297">y_2=m\left(m-1\right)x^{m-2}\ln{x}+mx^{m-2}+\left(m-1\right)x^{m-2} \\ \Rightarrow x^2y_2=m\left(m-1\right)x^m\ln{x}+\left(2m-1\right)x^m \\ \Rightarrow x^2y_2=m\left(m-1\right)y+\left(2m-1\right)\left(xy_1-my\right) \\ \Rightarrow2xy_2+x^2y_3=m\left(m-1\right)y_1+\left(2m-1\right)\left(y_1+xy_2-my_1\right) \\ \Rightarrow2xy_2+x^2y_3=m^2y_1-my_1+2my_1+2mxy_2-2m^2y_1-y_1-xy_2+my_1 \\ \Rightarrow2xy_2+x^2y_3=-m^2y_1+2my_1-y_1+2mxy_2-xy_2 \\ \therefore x^2y_3+2xy_2+y_1\left(1-m\right)^2+xy_2\left(1-2m\right)=0 </script></span></p>

<p><b>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</b></p>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-301">2xy_2+x^2y_3=m\left(m-1\right)y_1+\left(2m-1\right)\left(y_1+xy_2-my_1\right) </script></span>&nbsp;নির্ণয়ের জন্য ০২ নম্বর।</p>

<p><strong>বি:দ্রঃ&nbsp;</strong>যুক্তিসংগত যে কোনো নিয়ম গ্রহনযোগ্য।</p>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                                        <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 4</span>
                                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-303-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed equality" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-8643" style="width: 17.14em; x≤4 \\ \frac{x^3-16x^2+83x+k}{x^3-21x^2+140x-288}; x>4 \end {cases}</script></span></p>

<p>যদি ফাংশনটির&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-304-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="x equals 4" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-8752" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-children="0,2" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="width: 2.908em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.386em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.35em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-8753"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-8754" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-parent="3" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-8755" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="3" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-8756" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="2" data-semantic-parent="3" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-304">x=4 </script></span>&nbsp;বিন্দুতে লিমিটের অস্তিত্ব থাকে, তবে উক্ত লিমিট এবং k&nbsp;এর মান নির্ণয় কর।</p>

<p>ধরি,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-306-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed relation sequence with 3 elements" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-8850" style="width: 8.117em; top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 7.912em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-8990" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="102" data-semantic-parent="110" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-8991" data-semantic-type="fraction" data-semantic-role="vulgar" data-semantic-id="105" data-semantic-children="103,104" data-semantic-parent="110" data-semantic-complexity="5.6" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-8992" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="103" data-semantic-parent="105" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">20</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.65em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.448em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.053em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-308">\underset{h \to 0}{\lim} \frac{1-e^{-3h}}{20\ln{\left(1+h\right)}}=\underset{h \to 0}{\lim} \frac{1-\left(1-3h+\frac{\left(3h\right)^2}{2!}-\ldots\right)}{20\left(h-\frac{h^2}{2}+\frac{h^3}{3}-\frac{h^4}{4}+\ldots\right)}=\frac{3}{20} </script></span>&nbsp;[Ans.]&nbsp;</p>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-9185" data-semantic-type="prefixop" data-semantic-role="negative" data-semantic-id="30" data-semantic-children="23" data-semantic-content="22" data-semantic-parent="31" data-semantic-complexity="5" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9186" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="22" data-semantic-parent="30" data-semantic-operator="prefixop,−" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-9187" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="23" data-semantic-parent="30" data-semantic-complexity="2" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">140</span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9188" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="32" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-9189" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="24" data-semantic-parent="33" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.252em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-313">\therefore4^3-{16\times4}^2+83\times4+k=0\Rightarrow k=-140\ </script></span>&nbsp;[Ans.]</p>

<p><b>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</b></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-315-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="k equals negative 140" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-9238" data-semantic-type="relseq" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-children="0,4" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="10" style="width: 4.182em; <p><strong>বি.দ্রঃ&nbsp;</strong>যুক্তিসংগত যে কোনো নিয়ম গ্রহণযোগ্য।</p>

                                            </div>


                            </div>
                        </div>
                            <div class="row" style="margin-top:20px;">
                                <h2>Physics (3)</h2>
                            </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                                        <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 5</span>
                                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>2.5&nbsp;m&nbsp;দীর্ঘ একটি ইস্পাতের সুষম তারের ভর&nbsp;16&nbsp;g&nbsp;এবং ঘনত্ব&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-316-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="collapsed separator separated list of length 1" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-9245" style="width: 6.298em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.143em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1005.14em, 2.573em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="maction" id="MJX-Collapse-675" data-semantic-complexity="3"><span class="MathJax_HitBox" id="MathJax-HitBox-9246" style="border: 0px none; display: inline-block; <p>[<strong>বি.দ্রঃ </strong>একক না লিখলে বা ভুল একক লিখলে ০১ নম্বর কাটা যাবে।]</p>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 6</span>
                                                        <span style="color:green; font-weight:bold; float:right !important; ">             10/10</span>

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>200&nbsp;gm&nbsp;ভরের একটি বস্তু সরল ছন্দিত গতিতে গতিশীল। মধ্যাবস্থান হতে বস্তুটির যখন&nbsp;0.15&nbsp;m&nbsp;সরণ হয়, তখন এর উপর ক্রিয়ারত প্রত্যায়নী বলের মান&nbsp;0.3N&nbsp;। গতির দোলনকাল নির্ণয় কর।</p>

                                        </div>

<p>সরণ&nbsp;= x</p>

overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9915" data-semantic-type="relation" data-semantic-role="equality" data-semantic-id="1" data-semantic-parent="6" data-semantic-operator="relseq,=" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.98</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9917" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="7" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-9918" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9919" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="8" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-9920" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="4" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-9921" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="9" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-9922" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-parent="10" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-338">T = 1.98\ s\ </script></span>&nbsp;নির্ণয়ের জন্য ০৪ নম্বর।</p>

<p>[<strong>বি.দ্রঃ </strong>একক না লিখলে বা ভুল একক লিখলে ০১ নম্বর কাটা যাবে। সূত্র না লিখে সরাসরি মান বসালেও সূত্রের জন্য বরাদ্দকৃত নম্বর পাবে।]</p>

                                            </div>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7</span>
                                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
