font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10129" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="130" data-semantic-parent="132" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-10130" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="128" data-semantic-parent="132" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">A</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10131" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="multiplication" data-semantic-id="131" data-semantic-parent="132" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="infixop,⁢" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-10132" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="129" data-semantic-parent="132" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">Y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.56em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.559em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.453em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -5.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 6.753em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-340">\ell=\frac{FL}{AY}\ ;\ell=\frac{mgL}{AY}\ ;d\ell=\frac{\left(\rho Ay\right)g\ dy}{AY}\therefore d\ell=\frac{\rho g}{Y}\ ydy \\
\ell=\frac{\rho g}{Y}\int_{0}^{L}ydy  \\
\therefore\ell=\frac{\rho gL^2}{2Y} =\frac{\frac{m}{AL}gL^2}{2Y}=\frac{mgL}{2AY} 
</script></span></p>

<p><strong>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</strong></p>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-10230" data-semantic-type="prefixop" data-semantic-role="negative" data-semantic-id="7" data-semantic-children="6" data-semantic-content="5" data-semantic-parent="8" data-semantic-complexity="4"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-10231"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10232" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="5" data-semantic-parent="7" data-semantic-operator="prefixop,−" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10234" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="14" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-10235" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="9" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10236" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="15" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-10237" data-semantic-type="identifier" data-semantic-role="latinletter" data-semantic-font="italic" data-semantic-id="10" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10238" data-semantic-type="punctuation" data-semantic-role="dummy" data-semantic-id="16" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-added="true" data-semantic-operator="punctuated" data-semantic-complexity="1"></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-10239" data-semantic-type="text" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="11" data-semantic-parent="17" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; <p>[<strong>বি.দ্রঃ </strong>একক না লিখলে বা ভুল একক লিখলে ০১ নম্বর কাটা যাবে। সূত্র না লিখে সরাসরি মান বসালেও সূত্রের জন্য বরাদ্দকৃত নম্বর পাবে।]</p>

                                            </div>

                                <h2>Chemistry (3)</h2>

                                        </div>

position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-10420" data-semantic-complexity="1.5"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-10421"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-10422" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="19" data-semantic-parent="21" data-semantic-complexity="1.5" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-10423" data-semantic-complexity="1.5"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-10424"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-10425" data-semantic-type="number" data-semantic-role="integer" data-semantic-font="normal" data-semantic-id="20" data-semantic-parent="21" data-semantic-complexity="1.5" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">21</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-352">=2.7\times{10}^{-3}\times2\times6.023\times{10}^{23}=3.25\times{10}^{21} </script></span>&nbsp;টি।</p>

<p><strong>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</strong></p>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">21</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-355">=3.25\times{10}^{21} </script></span>&nbsp;টি&nbsp;নির্ণয়ের জন্য ০৩ নম্বর।</p>

<p>[<strong>বি.দ্রঃ </strong>একক না লিখলে বা ভুল একক লিখলে ০১ নম্বর কাটা যাবে।]</p>

                                            </div>
                                            <div class="alert" role="alert" style="width:100% !important; text-align:center; margin-bottom:0px;">
                                                

                                                <div class="text-center formBox" style="display:none;" maxlength="1000">
                                                    <div class="text-right counterBox" style="font-weight:bold;">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                                        <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9</span>
                                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>লুইস তত্ত্বানুসারে যৌগ/আয়নসমূহের অম্ল-ক্ষার ধর্ম ব্যাখ্যা কর।</p>

<p><b>(b)&nbsp;</b>CO&nbsp;অণু ক্ষেত্রে :&nbsp;CO&nbsp;অণুতে নিঃসঙ্গ ইলেকট্রন জোড় বর্তমান থাকায় এটির পক্ষে ইলেকট্রন জোড় দান সম্ভব।এ কারণে&nbsp;CO&nbsp;লুইস ক্ষার।<!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><span

 mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr m:val="roman"/><m:sty
    m:val="p"/></m:rPr> </m:r></span></m:oMath><![endif]--></p>

<p><b>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</b></p>

<p>লুইস তত্ত্বানুসারে যৌগ / আয়নসমূহের অম্ল-ক্ষার ধর্ম ব্যাখ্যার জন্য (২ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-370-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="times" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-10728" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="width: 0.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1000.49em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-10729"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-10730" data-semantic-type="operator" data-semantic-role="unknown" data-semantic-id="0" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.703em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-370">\times</script></span>&nbsp;৫) = ১০ নম্বর।</p>

                                            <span>Question 10</span>

<p>ধরি,&nbsp;Cl-35&nbsp;এর পরিমাণ x&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-379-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="therefore" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-10900" data-semantic-complexity="1" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1000.49em, 2.42em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-379">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;Cl-37&nbsp;এর পরিমাণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-380-Frame" tabindex="0" style="" role="application" aria-label="1 minus x" haslabel="true"><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-10903" data-semantic-type="infixop" data-semantic-role="subtraction" data-semantic-id="3" data-semantic-children="0,2" data-semantic-content="1" data-semantic-complexity="6" style="width: 2.256em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.846em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1001.8em, 2.215em, -999.998em); <p><strong>নম্বর বণ্টনঃ</strong></p>
